      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    POBMON  4
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    POKOTE  3
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    POKIBN  3
      *
     C                     CALL 'AAMRS5'  AAMRS6
      *
     C                     MOVELPOKOTE    @@KOTE  3
